title: Calexico's Joey Burns on losing yourself in art & writing 'El Mirador' (interview with The Current)
description:
Calexico's Joey Burns joins Mary Lucia to discuss house shoes, losing yourself in writing lyrics, and the influences that shaped their upcoming record, 'El Mirador'.

title: Superchunk - Endless Summer (live for The Current)
description:
Following the release of their 2022 album 'Wild Loneliness,' North Carolina's Superchunk join The Current to play "Endless Summer" from their new record. 

Plus, check out the bands full virtual session, including an interview with Superchunk's Mac McCaughan: https://youtu.be/jQOG6dhv8qs
